      "description": "Vehicle is in poor condition and priced accordingly. It shows heavy cosmetic wear inside and out, with noticeable blemishes, age-related deterioration, and signs of hard use. Expect mechanical issues or deferred maintenance, and this is best suited for a buyer looking for a budget vehicle, a project, or something to repair. Please do not expect a clean or trouble-free car, but it may still be useful for the right buyer at the right price.",
