      "description": "Budget-friendly and straightforward, this vehicle is an affordable opportunity for a buyer seeking basic transportation, a project, or a practical parts donor. It shows its age and wear, but it still offers solid value at an accessible price point. A sensible choice for someone who appreciates a no-nonsense deal and the chance to put a dependable vehicle back to work.",
